\c 8
\s Izenzo ezinhle zeN\nd kosi\nd* eyazenza kuIsrayeli enkangala
\p
\v 1 Yonke imithetho engikulaya yona lamuhla lizananzelela ukuyenza, ukuze liphile, lande, lingene lidle ilifa lelizwe, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo\x + 4.1.5.32,33.6.1-3.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo uzakhumbula indlela yonke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekukhokhele ngayo liminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala, ukuze ikuthobise\x + 1.3. 2.7. 29.5. Amos 2.10.\x*, ikuhlole\x + 8.16; Eks. 15.25.\x*, ukwazi okusenhliziyweni yakho, uba uzagcina imithetho yayo, loba hatshi\x + 2 Lan. 32.31.\x*.
\v 3 Yasikuthobisa, yakulambisa\x + Eks. 16.2,3.\x*, yakudlisa imana owawungayazi, laboyihlo babengayazi\x + Eks. 16.12,14,15,35.\x*, ukuze ikwazise ukuthi umuntu kaphili ngesinkwa sodwa, kodwa ngakho konke okuphuma emlonyeni weN\nd kosi\nd* umuntu uyaphila\x + Mat. 4.4. Luka 4.4.\x*.
\v 4 Izembatho zakho kaziguganga phezu kwakho, lonyawo lwakho kaluvuvukanga, le iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 29.5. Neh. 9.21.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho yazi enhliziyweni yakho ukuthi njengendoda ilaya indodana yayo, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iyakulaya\x + 11.2. Jobe 5.17. Zaga 3.11. Hos. 10.10. Heb. 12.5,6. 2 Sam. 7.14. Hlab. 89.32. Isam. 3.19.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho uzagcina imithetho yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukuhamba endleleni zayo, lokuyesaba\x + 5.33.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikungenisa elizweni elihle, ilizwe lezifula zamanzi, lemithombo lokujula okugobhoza ezihotsheni lezintabeni\x + 11.10-12.\x*;
\v 8 ilizwe lengqoloyi, \w lebhali\w**, lezivini, lemikhiwa, lezithelo \w zepomegranati\w**, ilizwe lezihlahla zemihlwathi zamafutha, loluju\x + Nani 20.5.\x*,
\v 9 ilizwe ozakudla kulo isinkwa kungekho ukusilela, ongayikuswela lutho kulo; ilizwe elilamatshe ayinsimbi, lelilezintaba elingagebha kuzo ithusi\x + 33.25.\x*.
\v 10 Usudlile wasutha, uzabusisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngelizwe elihle ekunike lona.
\v 11 Ziqaphele hlezi ukhohlwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngokungagcini imilayo yayo lezahlulelo zayo lezimiso zayo, engikulaya zona lamuhla.
\v 12 Hlezi lapho usudlile wasutha, usuwakhe izindlu ezinhle wahlala \add kuzo\x + 6.11,12. Dute. 28.47. 32.15. Zaga 30.9. Hos. 13.6.\x*\add*,
\v 13 sekwandile inkomo zakho lezimvu zakho, lesiliva legolide kwakho sekwandile, lakho konke olakho sekwandile,
\v 14 inhliziyo yakho ibisiziphakamisa\x + 1 Kor. 4.7.\x*, ubusukhohlwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyakukhupha elizweni leGibhithe, endlini yobugqili\x + Hlab. 78.11. 106.21.\x*,
\v 15 eyakukhokhela enkangala enkulu leyesabekayo\x + 1.19.\x*, \add okwakule\add*nyoka ezilokutshisa\x + Nani 21.6,8.\x* lezinkume\x + Hez. 2.6.\x* lomhlabathi owomileyo, lapho okwakungelamanzi khona\x + Hos. 13.5.\x*, eyakuvezela amanzi edwaleni lelitshe elilukhuni\x + Eks. 17.6. Nani 20.11.\x*,
\v 16 eyakudlisa imana enkangala, oyihlo ababengayazi, ukuze ikuthobise, lokuze ikuhlole\x + 8.3. Eks. 16.15.\x*, ikwenzele okuhle ekucineni kwakho\x + Jer. 24.5-7. Heb. 12.11.\x*,
\v 17 ubususithi enhliziyweni yakho: Amandla ami lokuqina kwesandla sami kungizuzele linotho.
\v 18 Kodwa uzakhumbula iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ngoba yiyo ekunika amandla okuzuza inotho\x + Zaga 10.22. Hos. 2.8.\x*, ukuze iqinise isivumelwano sayo eyasifungela oyihlo njengalamuhla\x + 7.8,12.\x*.
\v 19 Kuzakuthi-ke, nxa ukhohlwa lokukhohlwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ulandele abanye onkulunkulu, ubakhonze, ubakhothamele\x + 6.14.\x*, ngiyalifakazela lamuhla ukuthi lizabhubha lokubhubha\x + 4.26. 30.18.\x*.
\v 20 Njengezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ezichithileyo phambi kwenu, ngokunjalo lizabhubha, ngoba lingalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Dan. 9.11,12.\x*.
